sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as TaskUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant TaskCtrl as TaskController
participant TaskSvc as TaskService
participant OrgApi as OrganizationService
participant TaskDb as MongoTask
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant Worker as TaskFromFileWorker
User->>Client: Tao task thuong
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/tasks
Gateway->>TaskCtrl: createTask
TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: validate actor + payload
TaskSvc->>OrgApi: verify org/assignee
alt Hop le
  TaskSvc->>TaskDb: insert task
  TaskSvc-->>Client: 201 created
else Sai rule
  TaskSvc-->>Client: 400/403/404
end
User->>Client: Tao task tu file chat
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/tasks/from-chat-file
Gateway->>TaskCtrl: createTaskFromFile
TaskCtrl->>TaskSvc: publish async job
TaskSvc->>Queue: enqueue task.from.chat.file
TaskSvc-->>Client: 202 accepted
Queue->>Worker: consume + promote file + tao task
Worker->>TaskDb: persist result
